Plot: President Gilcrest and his trophy wife are living in the White House, with their overachieving daughter sidetracked by pregnancy, a couch potato hopeless son, a genius young son, and an odd middle school girl.
Title: 1600 Penn
Writer: Josh Gad, Jon Lovett, Jason Winer
Actors: Josh Gad, Jenna Elfman, Martha MacIsaac, André Holland
